* Dimension Table\nGranularity
** Granularity Options
***_ One row per entity (SCD Type 1)
***_ One row per entity per version (SCD Type 2)
***_ Periodic snapshots
** Must Align with Fact Table
***_ Fact surrogate key → must find in dim
***_ Transaction date must fall in validity
** SCD Type Alignment
***_ Type 1: current row only
***_ Type 2: versioned rows with validity
***_ Snapshot: periodic state capture
** Impact on Queries
***_ Join complexity increases with versioning
@endmindmap
